    "Some of these cases have Antitrust labeled as the nature of suit, so a ruling against the plainti in these cases indicated a conservative direction.",
    "Third, we used a legal search engine to identify an additional sample of cases, based on the search terms in Baye and Wright (2011).",
    "Each case was rst analyzed for its antitrust content.",
    "To be included in our data set, a decision needed to involve an action or claim by at least one party that asserted a violation of state or federal antitrust law.",
    "Some decisions that do not directly address substantive antitrust questions were included if they rule on procedural issues in favor of parties seeking antitrust enforcement or asserting antitrust claims, both because these rulings may be indicative of judges' larger views of antitrust law and because such procedural or arguably procedural questions can bear on parties' ability to assert antitrust claims successfully."
